                    >Third party verification and publishing</span
                  >
                  <p>
                    We provide support through verification and EPD publication. We will procure the relevant third-party verifier based on their expertise and project requirements.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class='col icon-with-text-style-01'>
              <div
