                            <i class='line-icon-Cursor-Click2 icon-extra-large text-base-color'></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-box-content">
                            <span class="d-inline-block alt-font text-dark-gray fw-600 mb-5px fs-20">Third party verification and publishing</span>
                            <p class="w-90 md-w-100">We provide support through verification and EPD publication. We will procure the relevant third-party verifier based on their expertise and project requirements.
</p>
                        </div>
